Package: tidycleanr
Type: Package
Title: Streamlining Data Cleaning for Everyday Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Christine", "Jacob",
      email = "christinejacob@usf.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Simple, consistent utilities for preparing messy tabular data. It can standardize column names, convert common types, 
        impute missing values with statistically relevant defaults, and remove duplicates across keys. Allows to clean data quicker, allowing
        dev to spend more time on analysis and fine-tuning.
